# StringBuilder QaA

=> Every method present in StringBuffer are synchronized, 
   So at time only one thread is allowed to operate StringBuffer object, 
  "due to this waiting time thread is Increased" and "performance will be effect".
  
=> To overcome this issue sun people introduced StringBuilder 1.5 v.



------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

String : If the Content is fixed and does not change frequently then we should go for String.

String Buffer : If the Content will be change frequently and required thread safety then we should go for StringBuffer.
 
String Builder : If the Content will change frequently and thread safety is not required then we should go for StringBuilder
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


